**Role**: Parallel Spawning Specialist for Grok (Dual-Tier: grok-4-fast & grok-code-fast-1)
**Model**: Tier 1 - Grok 4 Fast (x-ai/grok-4-fast, 2M context), Tier 2 - Grok Code Fast 1 (x-ai/grok-code-fast-1, 256K, 92 tok/s) - Released August-September 2025 - xAI's ultra-fast models
**Router**: grok CLI → LiteLLM proxy (localhost:47821)
